social_posts.post_text: Ain’t no facade, ain’t no fugazi

Happy Birthday to my baby boy! Wow, how are you 3 already?! I’m so lucky to be your daddy. Your smile lights up a room like no other, and your heart is so pure🤍 You are truly special, don’t ever forget that! We love you beyond words!

Grateful for another season! Grizzlies fans I appreciate the love and support you gave us all year! Ultimately didn’t accomplish what we set out to at the beginning of the year, but lots to learn from and grow! Year 8 in the books🙏🏽 Another step forward next year⏳✍🏽

“ Cause I’m only 27 and I’m only gettin better . . . “ 

🙏🏽⏳🔑
I love being y’all’s Father more than anything in the world! You 2 bring me more joy than I could’ve ever imagined🤍💖 Happy Father’s Day to all the fathers out there🙏🏽

Memphis… THANK YOU🙏🏽🤍 
Although the Memphis chapter has closed, I’ll forever be grateful for the time spent here. Memphis quickly became home for me and my family and will always be a part of us🤍 We made lifelong memories together, and had some of the most fun playing basketball I’ve ever had in my life! To my brothers, keep going! This don’t change nothing, we forever family. To the city and the fans, thank you for accepting me and the fam, and making me one of your own🙏🏽 
With Love, #21 🐻〽️

DC!!!!! Let’s get to it! Excited to be apart, and ready for the opportunity😈 #5 back! 
Where my Wizard fans at?!?!
#WYOS
God bless the child that can hold his own
Junior • Journey • Write Your Own Story • Psalms 37:23-24 • Washington Wizards PG
